EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO TAXATION -- PROPERTY SUBJECT TO TAXATION
***
1 This act would authorize a host city or town to impose a two percent (2%) tax on the
2 endowment of a private institution of higher education that is in excess of one billion dollars
3 ($1,000,000,000), to be used only for the host public school district.
4 This act would take effect upon passage.
